title: TMS’ Gossage visits with trophy
text:
TMS’ Gossage visits with trophy TMS’ Gossage visits with trophy Buy Photo 
JASON DELLA ROSA / HERALD DEMOCRAT — Texas Motor Speedway president Eddie Gossage stopped by the Herald Democrat offices on Tuesday with the AAA Texas 500 trophy for the Nov. 8 race. "Our April race is early in the season and the November race is so late they have such a different feel," Gossage said. "The intensity ramps up every week." By Jason Della RosaHerald Democrat 
Texas Motor Speedway president Eddie Gossage stopped by the Herald Democrat offices on Tuesday with the AAA Texas 500 trophy for the Nov. 8 race. 
“Our April race is early in the season and the November race is so late they have such a different feel,” Gossage said. “The intensity ramps up every week.”
